$ Oracle redo log files
@ redo log files

Redo log files are needed for *instance recovery* and *media recovery*.

The location of the redo log files is specified with the → development/databases/Oracle/adminstration/init-parameters/log_archive_dest_n[log_archive_dest_n] init parameter.

